summary:
Main theme - \"Shen Khar Venakhi\"-Medieval Georgian iambiko and chant, written by the King Demetre the I (1097-1156). 
The chant is one of the best examples of medieval Georgian polyphonic music.
Performed by \" Georgian Voices\"
